  "riverbank": {
    "id": "Riverbank",
    "name": "Riverbank",
    "description": "You manage to deal a wounding crack to the giant crab's shell, driving it into a rage as it flees through the forest. With a moment of peace, you take stock of your surroundings. And if the amount of crabs on the river's shore are any indication, this might be the enormous crab nest you had heard about. You can't even tell where the shore meets the riverbank with the amount of crabs around here. The giant crab's trail is easy to spot, but it's just not possible to follow it without getting attacked by the smaller crabs. You will likely nead to get through  multiple groups of them on your way",
